name: Portrait of Chihuahua, Nicky
description:
Little Chihuahua, 6 years old, named Nicky.

Very possesive to his pawrents, Lic.

Nicky very protective to his mother too.

When I took this photo, I must move very slightly because Nicky will bark and going to bite me if I move to much and suddenly.

Live long, Nicky!
